features: 【HIGH TEMPERATURE HIGH PRESSURE】Steam cleaner heats up quickly in 3 minutes, 1050W high power can produce high temperature of 275℉ and pressure up to 3.0bar steam for up to 10 minutes! Easily clean oil, dust and stains that regular cleaning can't dissolve, make your home look brand new.

【NATURAL & HARMLESS】The handheld steam cleaner is free of chemical fumes and residue, and only uses high temperature and high pressure steam to clean, which is safe and reliable. The pressurized steam cleaner also features safety lock technology to prevent children from operating it incorrectly, a healthy and friendly steam cleaner for children and pets.

【MULTIPLE SURFACE STEAM CLEANER】This steamer for cleaning with 9 cleaning tools. Different accessories can be used to remove grease and grime from tiles, sinks, kitchen stoves, bathrooms, floors, windows, mirrors, toilets, pet mattresses, curtains, car seats, upholstery and other hard-to-reach areas. Save your time by treating multiple areas of your home with one steamer for cleaning.

【Large Capacity & Fast Heating】350ml water tank capacity (recommend filling 200ml with water) can provide continuous steam for about 10 minutes without adding water frequently. Only need about 3 minutes to produce pressurized hot steam quickly.

【LARGE CAPACITY WATER TANK】The handheld steam cleaner comes with a large 350ml (11.83oz) (recommended load capacity up to 280ml (9.46oz)), the extra-large water tank allows you to focus on cleaning instead of refilling frequently.

【WARM TIPS】If you can't open the lid after use, it's because the temperature of the residual steam inside the can is still too high. Please: 1. unplug it first 2. exhaust the residual steam completely or wait for the steam to cool down 3. open the lid and add water into the steam cleaner.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Pressure and Heating
reviews.reviewText: This steam cleaner came with all aforementioned accessories. The pressure and amount of heat are great and help clean hard to reach areas. I used it to clean an old exersaucer from my 2-year old for my 6-month old and the bouncer looks brand new (excluding the seat cover which was machine-washed). There’s a safety function to keep the lid closed when water shouldn’t be added or it’s very hot. It will act as a continuous spinning mechanism until all the steam/water has been used. Be sure to let it cool down before adding water when the cap is released or it will boil out of the top and spray everywhere. I made this mistake while paying more attention to what my toddler was doing than the heated tool in my hand. Overall, this is a great buy and was very affordable.
